frames.caption: A fluffy gray cat with large green eyes sits on a windowsill, gazing curiously at a fish-shaped clock. Sunlight streams through the window, casting a warm glow over the cozy room. Books and a stuffed fish toy are visible in the background, adding to the homely atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a cozy, well-lit room with a window that allows sunlight to filter in, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. A curious cat is the focal point, observing a uniquely designed clock shaped like a fish.
